1. Verify EtherChannel Configuration:
Devices: SpringCore1, SpringCore2, DataCenter
# Verify EtherChannel Status
show etherchannel summary
show interfaces port-channel

2. Verify VLAN Configuration:
Devices: All Switches (SpringCore1, SpringCore2, Floor1, Floor2, Floor3, DataCenter)
# Verify VLANs
show vlan brief
# Verify VTP Mode
show vtp status


3. Verify Spanning Tree Configuration:
Devices: All Switches
# Verify STP
show spanning-tree

4. Verify IPv4 Addressing and OSPF Configuration:
Devices: SpringCore1, SpringCore2, SpringR1, SpringR2
# Verify IP Address
show ip interface brief
# Verify OSPF Neighbors
show ip ospf neighbor
# Verify OSPF Routes
show ip route ospf

5. Verify HSRP Configuration:
Devices: SpringCore1, SpringCore2

# Verify HSRP Status
show standby brief

6. Verify IPv6 Addressing and OSPFv3 Configuration:
Devices: SpringCore1, SpringCore2, SpringR1, SpringR2
# Verify IPv6 Address
show ipv6 interface brief
# Verify OSPFv3 Neighbors
show ipv6 ospf neighbor
# Verify OSPFv3 Routes
show ipv6 route ospf

7. Verify NAT Configuration:
Devices: SpringR1, SpringR2
# Verify NAT Translations
show ip nat translations
# Verify NAT Statistics
show ip nat statistics

8. Verify Floating Static Routes:
Devices: SpringCore1, SpringCore2
# Verify Routing Table
show ip route

9. Verify DHCP Configuration on ISP Interfaces:
Devices: SpringR1, SpringR2
# Verify DHCP Assigned IP
show ip interface brief

10. Verify Port Security Configuration:
Devices: Floor1, Floor2, Floor3
# Verify Port Security
show port-security
show port-security interface <interface>

11. Verify ACL Configuration:
Devices: All Devices with ACLs
# Verify ACLs
show access-lists
12. Verify SSH Configuration:
Devices: All Devices
# Verify SSH
show ip ssh

13. General Connectivity Tests:
Devices: Any Device
# Ping Tests for IPv4
ping <IP Address>
# Ping Tests for IPv6
ping ipv6 <IPv6 Address>
# Traceroute Tests for IPv4
traceroute <IP Address>
# Traceroute Tests for IPv6
traceroute ipv6 <IPv6 Address>



